title: Lovely 1 Bedroom in Canoga Park + Controlled Access + Ceiling Fan
posting_body: ['Unit Availability: August 17, 2022', 'Here at Roscoe Terrace you will find comforts such an inviting pool and lush landscape.', ' Do you spend a lot of time in the kitchen?', ' If so, you have the choice of an apartment with stainless steel appliances.', 'Roscoe Terrace is located in between the 101 & 118 freeways, just moments to Westfield Shopping mall, Home Depot, Costco, Supermarkets & many more local conveniences.', 'On site management and maintenance are here to make you feel right at home.', ' Contact them today!', 'show contact info', '<URL>/', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES', '- Air Conditioning', '- Ceiling Fan', '- Disposal', '- Window Coverings', '- Stainless Steel Appliances (In Select Units)', '- Hardwood Inspired Flooring', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES', '- Controlled Access/Gated', '- On-Site Maintenance', '- 1 Assigned Parking Space (In Select Units)', '- On-Site Management', '- Courtyard', '- Swimming Pool', '- Pool Lounge Area', '21225 Roscoe Boulevard', 'Canoga Park, CA', '91304', 'Square Footage Is Approximate.', 'Price and availability are subject to change.', 'Interior Photos may not be of exact unit.', "Close to 27, 101 Freeway, The Tasting Room at 8one8 Brewing, Bazillw, Henri's Restaurant, JOEY Woodland Hills, The Cheesecake Factory, AMC Promenade 16, Warner Center Park, Valley Soccer Center, Planet Fitness, Lanark Park, Walmart, Westfield Topanga & The Village, Amazon Fresh, The Home Depot, Parkhill School, Nevada Ave ES, Canoga Park HS, University of Topanga, National University, Reseda, Winnetka, Chatsworth, Warner Center, Northridge, West Hills, Woodland Hills"]
